version_description: Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Person to person is now real-time capable. If the receiving bank is able to receive real-time payments, the recipient will have the money available within minutes!
We fixed a bug that may have caused you to be unenrolled from FirstGlance.  We also made some improvements to the performance and stability of Zelle.  Check it out!
